# Cryptocurrency Price Tracker

## Tools Requirements

* npm

## Javascript Library Requirements

* webpack
* jquery
* vuejs

## How to reproduce the final add-on file ?

```shell
unzip cryptocurrency-price-tracker-source.zip
cd cryptocurrency-price-tracker/

# Initializing npm packages & environments
npm install --verbose

# Generate final add-on directory
make prod

# Generate final add-on zip file
make zip

# Then cryptocurrency-price-tracker.zip is generated final add-on file
ls cryptocurrency-price-tracker.zip
```
